ue for the IACT\nVERITAS. In particular, we focus on how our method framework employs a\ndimension for gamma-hadron separation parameters in order to improve\nsensitivity on extended sources.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Aug 2021 19:09:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-19"}
