atter, both for Schwarzschild and\nfor Schwarzschild-like wormholes. This reinforces the supposition that a\nphantom fluid is always present for wormholes in this context.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Aug 2021 00:10:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 1 Sep 2021 16:59:30 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 11 Oct 2021 13:26:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-12"}
