. To illustrate our recommendations, we present some results for\nflow-based programming in our Industrial DevOps project Titan, where we employ\nflow-based programming for the Industrial Internet of Things.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Aug 2021 10:25:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-19"}
